frames.caption: A majestic peacock stands gracefully in a sunlit forest clearing, its vibrant plumage shimmering in the golden light. The sunlight filters through the trees, casting a warm glow on the peacock and the surrounding foliage. Bright orange flowers add a splash of color to the serene woodland scene.
frames.description: The scene is set in a tranquil forest clearing, where a peacock is the focal point, bathed in sunlight. The atmosphere is peaceful and enchanting, with the interplay of light and shadow creating a magical ambiance.

frames.caption: A woman stands gracefully in a forest, wearing a dress adorned with peacock feathers. Sunlight filters through the trees, casting a warm glow around her. She poses with her hands near her head, exuding confidence and elegance.
frames.description: The scene is set in a mystical forest with sunlight streaming through the trees, creating a magical atmosphere. The woman is the focal point, dressed in a vibrant peacock-themed gown, surrounded by nature.
